itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T02:55:47.000Z","msg":"恭喜蔡若蓮之子魂歸閪天 咁就叫歹毒?<br />\n<br />\n你班濕尻高官呢幾年做d野又叫做咩呢?<br />\n<br />\n而家死左個仔咪便宜左你啦, 報應陸續有黎啊"},{"pid":"9ed0e3e3234114dc8bfca944b87eaa70c2dd3d3e","tid":391463,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T03:05:21.000Z","msg":"費事被當事人委託法律部門（e.g. 律政署）告誹謗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe06daff38367aa28ac64011dfff6a5613cde68","tid":391463,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:18:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a11199dddcdbbd9c0dd5590fe5f5e4702cce01c","tid":391463,"uid":53978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:24:12.000Z","msg":"係香港早死係好事 尤其有個咁嘅老母<br />\n受咗25年苦仲唔夠咩 早死早投胎仲幸福<br />\n咁開心嘅事絕對值得慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c290740a75a24bebd1018e94a58f9040409bc78f","tid":391463,"uid":53207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:51:27.000Z","msg":"我諗正苦係執著緊個匪字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講真歸西呢句冇乜問題<br />\n最多叫做口臭啲"},{"pid":"42da12c7ca85719c05629c1265e0cea9f470005c","tid":391463,"uid":78412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T14:55:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得永生 或者去極樂世界 好多人都係認為好嘢嚟，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">用恭喜依個字眼至多話不恰當。<br />\n我真係睇唔到幸災樂禍喎，</span><br />\n<br />\n每人價值觀唔同，<br />\n有人認為死係悲傷嘅事 ，<br />\n有人認為係好事真係值得恭喜，<br />\n香港幾時變到連少少言論自由都冇？<br />\n<br />\n點解要講道用恭喜依個字係十惡不赦 ？<br />\n你唔鍾意個用字最多話人冇禮貌姐。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁都話睇唔到幸災樂禍喎, 你唔係盲目到自己都呃埋呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n恭喜喎, 大佬, 係恭喜喎"},{"pid":"c4c244846509fff5a556d71b95ba3edaf326c1e1","tid":391463,"uid":56999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:10:34.000Z","msg":"有時真係忍唔住笑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/15555/production/_97718378_1123795.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef-1.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F624%2Fcpsprodpb%2F15555%2Fproduction%2F_97718378_1123795.jpg&h=3b04d906&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"828fb23f29eff4bd6c7719b7d9115a093bba9e53","tid":391463,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:12:54.000Z","msg":"每年都要記念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今年第一年更要為大家留下一個深刻印象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853d211fe6125b9bb7774fb057000a55cd867153","tid":391463,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T15:15:16.000Z","msg":"蓮又過年<br />\n共慶歡樂年年"}]}